episodes.title: I Think I JOINED A CULT!!!
episodes.description: Mimi attends a QHHT (Quantum Healing Hypnosis Technique) retreat in Asheville, NC & things get a little culty with messages from aliens & Jesus to a cacao ceremony with chanting.

episodes.title: How I Almost Joined a Cult ~ solo-female vanlife
episodes.description:
Mimi enjoys her last day with Stormy & Winnie in Sedona, Arizona with cold plunging in the river at Grasshopper Point in the Coconino Forest.
After they part ways Mimi heads south to Felicity, AZ/CA to learn about the history of cults & parachuting! 
She leaves unscathed & discovers a labyrinth in the middle of the desert!
